title: Eclectic Coffeehouse Studio and Gallery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Take-out, Bakery, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little coffeehouse and cafe that showcases local artists and provides art classes as well as weekday lunch 11:30am -3pm. Serves one meat dish daily but other menu items are vegan aside from the yogurt dressing and a cookie. Soups are based with fresh veggies and coconut milk. Fresh baked vegan goods daily. Locally roasted coffee. Free Wi-Fi.
